@Protonstar5 Hello Protonstar,
we have replied to your DM.
Thank you

@Ethan_Travels Hello Ethan, we sincerely apologize for the delay on handling your case and assure you that it is not forgotten. 
We kindly ask you to wait for our contact.
Thank you.

@dhteodoro Olá Douglas, pedimos desculpas pela demora na nossa resposta.
Verificamos que entretanto o seu pedido de alteração foi tratado por outra via.
Caso possamos ser úteis em qualquer outra questão, por favor, disponha. Obrigada.

@jnfigueira Olá juan,
Informamos que respondemos à sua DM.
Obrigad

@DennyDuong4 Hello Denny,
Please let us know your booking reference and the change you want so that we can verify this situation. We recommend that you do so by private message due to confidentiality reasons.
Thank you

@MattLeRoss @bookingcom Hello Matt, 
Travel agencies were already informed of the procedures.
Thank you.

@fenner_michael Michael,
Complaints are being analyzed by chronological order and due to a very high demand, they are taking longer to be completed. If you don't receive a reply until December 1st (1 month after the submission), please let us know. 
We thank you for your understanding.

@MattLeRoss @bookingcom Hello Matt, 
That situation must be dealt directly with the agency in which you purchased your ticket. We apologize for not being able to assist you any further, and request that you insist with them. 
Thank you.

@Bast_DS Olá Bastien,
De modo a verificar a situação, por favor indique-nos o código da sua reserva. Recomendamos que o faça por mensagem privada devido a razões de confidencialidade de dados.
Obrigado

